data.description: LAKE LIFE DOESN'T GET MUCH BETTER THAN THIS!...This 2 BD/2.5 BA multi-level townhome is perfectly placed amongst the Tsala Apopka Chain of Lakes, in the WATERFRONT, MAINTENANCE-FREE community of Cypress Cove. Upon arrival you can just sense that water is nearby with the Key West architectural style of the exterior, especially the spindle & corbel adorned front porch. NEW ROOF in October 2023. The interior of the home features the common area downstairs with laminate flooring, a half bath, a living room/dining room combo & a slider that opens to the screen enclosed porch. The kitchen features a breakfast bar, granite countertop, tiled backsplash & a closet pantry. For dramatic effect, a SPIRAL STAIRCASE takes you to 2 bedrooms, BOTH WITH ENSUITES on the upper level. The master bedroom features a slide that opens to a balcony for evening cocktails, a good read or just a quiet place to unwind & dream about which lake you are going to fish on next. Cypress Cove Community offers a pool, gazebo & a private boat ramp. The boat ramp is on a canal that provides DIRECT ACCESS to Little Lake Spivey directly behind the community, Big Lake Spivey to the east & out to the rest of the chain of lakes. Conveniently, Big Lake Henderson is directly across Gulf to Lake Highway, where a public boat ramp is located as well. Jump on the Withlacoochee State Trail nearby for biking, skating or taking your dog for a quiet walk. If indoor activity is your thing, then you’re in luck. Only 1 mile to Downtown Inverness which serves as the county seat. Only 5 minutes to Liberty & Wallace Brooks Parks, shopping, restaurants & the Historic Valerie Theatre. A FREE 1-year HOME WARRANTY for PEACE OF MIND is offered as a GIFT to the FUTURE BUYER at closing!
